{
  "stem": "22047.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, with Marge this time, and boy, had she changed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But she was a doll in high school, a real doll.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I-- I-- I liked her a lot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Model building.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I made things out of wood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Really, I've-- I've loved wood most of my life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And art.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I like to draw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, Marge has-- has some of my drawings that I made when I was a youngster.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sports.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I love baseball, love football, swimming.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I learned to swim when I was a Boy Scout, when I was 11.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was a-- a hard-- a hard learn though.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] We were on a-- a-- a camp, an encampment one year, northeast of Santa Barbara, in the Santa Ynez Valley.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were camped near the Santa Ynez River, and I didn't really know how to swim very well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'd taken some lessons, but.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One of the guys that-- that was sort of my overseer-- he was older than I was-- Jerry was his name.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He said, jump in, and I'll head for that rock over there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so it was probably no more than 20 feet wide there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I got over to this rock, and somebody had come in in front of me, so I couldn't get out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so I started floundering around in the water, and Jerry jumped in and hauled me out, and then he threw me back in the water.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I learned to swim.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I became a pretty good swimmer from then on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, in-- in grammar school particularly, there was this teacher who I dearly loved.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she-- we hit it off quite well.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
